parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping or Failure to Engage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or failure to engage can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in a particular gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates or slips when shifting gears
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the transmission fails to engage into gear
the vehicle is stuck in a particular gear
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Neutral or Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended neutral or loss of power can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

the vehicle loses power or acceleration
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The jerking or lunging when shifting can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The transmission jerks or lunges when shifting gears
the vehicle feels like it has been rear-ended
the transmission shifts harshly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The software or electronic issues can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

the dashboard lights up

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine fire can cause significant damage to the vehicle and potentially harm occupants or other road users.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in addressing the recall issue can lead to potential safety risks, such as engine stalling, and may result in costly repairs.
